title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: The moment is ripe for stripping away thoughts and possessions that are weighing you down and keeping you back. Perhaps you are working too hard and carrying too much stress in your body. Or, your mind overflows with endless harsh critiques about yourself and your own prospects. Similarly, you could be just as overwhelmed by too much stuff in your closets, cupboards, or drawers. Returning to basics and purging outworn items from your life is immensely liberating now. Eliminating clutter gives you more room and energy for the people and things that matter the most. Never forget laughter lightens the load. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
